Multivariable Calculus | Double integrals over rectangular regions.

\begin{array}{rl}\n\iint_{R} f d A & =\int_{a}^{b} \int_{c}^{d} f(x, y) d y d x \\\n& =\int_{c}^{d} \int_{a}^{b} f(x, y) d x d y \\\na & b\n\end{array}[imath]\iint_{R} f d A & =\int_{a}^{b} \int_{c}^{d} f(x, y) d y d x [/imath] [imath]& =\int_{c}^{d} \int_{a}^{b} f(x, y) d x d y [/imath] [imath]a & b[/imath]
